  "description": "Otrium FX chain demo — 3 bass engines lock into a tight isosceles triangle. Narrow 75° phase skew gives the cross-ducking a focused swing rather than even distribution; medium pump rate (2 Hz, free) keeps the low-end articulate without thinning it out. Use for sub-heavy contexts where a single sub voice would muddy. Otrium config embedded under Ogre's parameter block.",
